  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个证书管理的状态图，核心状态包括未初始化、初始化中、已初始化、重新配置和续期这几个关键节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Uninitialized",
        "Initializing",
        "Initialized",
        "Reconfig",
        "Renew"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先把起点指向未初始化状态。然后初始化操作是从未初始化到初始化中吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Uninitialized",
        "Initializing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，InitializeCA触发后会进入Initializing。另外还有一个特殊路径：未初始化可以直接跳转到重新配置状态，通过UpdateConfiguration触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Uninitialized",
        "Reconfig",
        "InitializeCA",
        "UpdateConfiguration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了起点到Uninitialized，以及Uninitialized到Initializing、Uninitialized到Reconfig的转换。那Reconfig之后怎么返回？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Uninitialized",
        "Initializing",
        "Reconfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Reconfig完成后return回到未初始化。关键是已初始化状态——它是个枢纽，RenewIntermediate触发续期，Stop则回到未初始化，UpdateConfiguration也能进入重新配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initialized",
        "Reconfig",
        "Uninitialized",
        "Renew",
        "Stop",
        "UpdateConfiguration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "已初始化到初始化中有一条标记INVALID的线，这是什么意思？是错误路径还是特殊处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initialized",
        "Initializing",
        "INVALID"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "那是无效转换，理论上不应该发生，但我们要显式标出来。还有，初始化完成时InitializeCA complete进入已初始化，续期完成后return也回到已初始化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initializing",
        "Initialized",
        "Renew",
        "InitializeCA complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已画好Initialized相关的所有转换。最后确认一下：Initializing、Reconfig、Renew都能通过Stop回到未初始化，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initializing",
        "Reconfig",
        "Renew",
        "Uninitialized",
        "Stop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，所有运行中状态都能被Stop终止回未初始化。另外注意Uninitialized到Initialized直接转换也是INVALID，这个别忘了标。",
      "elements_involved": [
